name: Naruto | Style LoRA
description:
Feel free to follow me on Twitter at Tacki_NO, and if you feel like saying thank you or you want to say hello, leave me a few hearts or dm on Discord at Tacki ●﹏●#2322

For those that would like to go the extra mile and support the creation of my models and their updates, please check out my ko-fi, where I'll be posting early access content, exclusive content surrounding models, things I'm working on, and more!

All models I make will ALWAYS BE FREE.


Now without further ado
Welcome to my first model. Based on the style of Masashi Kishimoto's Naruto, the number one hyperactive knucklehead ninja!

Thank you for your time and consideration! 😀

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
How to use LoRA

  • Make sure to change the weight (by default, it's :1 which is usually too high). I recommend you keep the weight around :0.5 to 0.9 for the best results. I found the best results at :0.9 and 0.8

What to Know

  • V2 is a merger between V1 and an unreleased iteration of the LoRA. The unreleased iteration was trained on Lykon's AnyLoRA - Checkpoint.

Where it also works

  • The LoRA has been tested on AOM2SFW, AnythingV5,
